## Description {#details}

This class provides methods to extract traceback table data from a buffer.

The various accessors may reference the buffer provided via the constructor.

Definition at line 902 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/object/xcoffobjectfile-h">XCOFFObjectFile.h</a>.

## Public Static Functions

### create() {#ad2c9fd0ee3e91f844a281fc9af7f57c9}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype={<>Expected&lt; XCOFFTracebackTable &gt; llvm::object::XCOFFTracebackTable::create (<a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/target/lib/target/aarch64/aarch64promoteconstant-cpp/#a90f8350fecae261c25be85d38b451bff">const</a> uint8&#95;t &#42; Ptr, uint64&#95;t &amp; Size, bool Is64Bits=false)</>}
  labels = {["static"]}>
Parse an <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/xcoff">XCOFF</a> Traceback Table from <em>Ptr</em> with <em>Size</em> bytes.

Returns an <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/object/xcofftracebacktable">XCOFFTracebackTable</a> upon successful parsing, otherwise an <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/error">Error</a> is returned.


<ParametersList title="Parameters">
<ParametersListItem name="[in] Ptr">A pointer that points just past the initial 4 bytes of zeros at the beginning of an <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/xcoff">XCOFF</a> Traceback Table.</ParametersListItem>
<ParametersListItem name="[inout] Size">A pointer that points to the length of the <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/xcoff">XCOFF</a> Traceback Table. If the <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/xcoff">XCOFF</a> Traceback Table is not parsed successfully or there are extra bytes that are not recognized, <em>Size</em> will be updated to be the size up to the end of the last successfully parsed field of the table.</ParametersListItem>
</ParametersList>

Declaration at line <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/object/xcoffobjectfile-h/#l00934">934</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/object/xcoffobjectfile-h">XCOFFObjectFile.h</a>, definition at line <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/object/xcoffobjectfile-cpp/#l01450">1450</a> of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/object/xcoffobjectfile-cpp">XCOFFObjectFile.cpp</a>.
</MemberDefinition>
